list.abstract: Eventually是涂议嘉演唱的歌曲，由涂议嘉作词作曲。
Eventually，英语单词，主要用作副词，作副词时译为“最后，终于”。

yingyinNormal.en: Boyfriend and girlfriend right now! No. Boyfriend and girlfriend eventually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 马上开始男女朋友关系！不。最后我们还是会成为男女朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually, the two of you are gonna have to work out your issues.
yingyinNormal.zh: 反正最后你们俩得解决你们的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: But eventually you'll just get the hang of it, just practice makes it perfect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过最后你会熟练掌握的，熟能生巧嘛！

yingyinNormal.en: But you know what? I did. Eventually, I did. Okay? So it is possible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是后来呢？我背叛他了，最后还是背叛他了，明白吗？所以这很有可能。

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, the guy's a secondary character, is just a, you know, complication you eventually kill off. When?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不过是个二等货，不过是最后要被你打败的。什么时候？

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually, I realized the song was about you, and like that earworm, I can't get you out of my heart.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后我终于发现，这歌和你有关，你是我挥之不去的耳虫，久久盘旋在心口。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually, it kind of burns out. But hopefully what you're left with is trust and security and, well, in the case of my ex-wife, lesbianism.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后激情很快就退去，但双方仍保有信赖，安全感和以我前妻为例，女同志主义。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon will move out eventually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿终究会搬出去的。

yingyinNormal.en: Your luck will run out, eventually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的好运迟早会用完。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually needs to become immediately.
yingyinNormal.zh: "最终"需要转化为"立刻"才行。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: All of us must face this truth eventually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们所有人都最终得面对这一事实。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. But eventually the party was over. Achoo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，但结果派对还是结束了。阿嚏。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually, we all become white ashes, Sidao.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最终我们都会化为尘土，似道。

yingyinNormal.en: My father's disease eventually outran the cure. For goodness sake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我父亲的病最终复发了，天哪。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: He is? Eventually. I mean, you see the way the man eats.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的吗？总有一天啊。你看看他的饮食习惯。

yingyinNormal.en: The hope has been that you'd eventually bend to public opinion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她的本意其实是你最终能变得正常一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Eventually, we did make it to the top, and we stayed there for 25 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最终，我们终于攀上了巅峰，并且保持了25年之久。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, but Ross, eventually you and I are gonna be dating. Really? We are?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，但我们迟早会约会。是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And once he moves through this, we will eventually be able to be okay again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等他想通以后，我们之间就又会变好的

yingyinNormal.en: But eventually you saw it, I mean, you actually saw it. Right? Never in the flesh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你亲眼见过它，真的看过，对吗？我从没见过它。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: in the end, especially after a long delay, dispute, or series of problems

examination_example.sentence: Likewise, automation should <highlight>eventually</highlight> boost productivity, stimulate demand by driving down prices, and free workers from hard, boring work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 同样，自动化最终应该会提高生产率，通过压低价格来刺激需求，并将工人从艰苦、枯燥的工作中解放出来。

examination_example.sentence: There will <highlight>eventually</highlight> come a day when The New York Times ceases to publish stories on newsprint.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 终有一天，《纽约时报》将停止在新闻纸上发表报道。

examination_example.sentence: About a quarter of all Italian immigrants, for example, <highlight>eventually</highlight> returned to Italy for good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，大约四分之一的意大利移民最终永远回到了意大利。
